Save file structure should be something like this

Inventory data format
4 bytes total size
4 bytes Number of items
list of item data

Item data format
4 bytes total size
4 bytes item ID
1 byte bool in use
Modifiers etc etc


Area data format



Begin save data file

0xEA7ADEADBEA57 Magic number
4 bytes total size of save file


Player data
4 bytes total size
4 bytes class ID
4 bytes location ID
4 bytes position X
4 bytes position Y
Inventory Data


Permanent entity data
4 bytes total size
4 bytes entity base ID
4 bytes location ID
4 bytes position X
4 bytes position Y
Modifiers etc etc
Inventory Data

Area data
4 bytes total size
4 bytes number of areas
